snippet.title: Assault Android Cactus PS4 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Assault Android Cactus is now on PS4 at the Playstation Store!
https://store.playstation.com/ 
Assault Android Cactus is an arcade style twin stick shooter set in a vivid sci fi universe.

Pick from a colourful roster of synthetic heroines and dive in guns blazing against a mechanical army in transforming arena style levels where only your skill, wits and reflexes will get you through.

Also available on Windows, OSX, and Linux
http://store.steampowered.com/app/250110
https://www.humblebundle.com/store/p/assaultandroidcactus_storefront

For more information please visit http://www.AssaultAndroidCactus.com

Follow us on Twitter and Facebook
https://twitter.com/AndroidCactus
https://www.facebook.com/AssaultAndroidCactus
